  <summary>5/25/2001--Introduced.
School and Day-Care Lead-Based Paint Reduction Act of 2001 - Authorizes the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development to make matching grants to States, local governments, and local educational agencies to evaluate and reduce lead-based paint hazards at public elementary schools and licensed child day-care facilities.</summary>
